title: Ep. 657 - Bhide Scolds Tapu - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Tapu enters the tuition class late and gets scolded by Bhide. But when Tapu gives his excuse, everyone starts laughing in the class. Bhide asks for Tapu for his homework which shocks him as the homework is complete.

title: Ep. 658 - Tapu Sena's Adamant Decision - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Tapu Sena agrees among themselves that if anyone asks them to study or go for tuitions on a holiday, they will say a strict no, be it anyone. Will Bhide agree to this or will he complain to the parents?

title: Ep. 659 - Tapu And Daya's Plan - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Tapu scares Jethalal right in the morning. When he is about to scold Tapu, Daya comes out of nowhere and scares him again. He starts yelling at both of them and asks them what is the reason to do all this in the morning.

title: Ep. 660 - Jethalal's Past Comes To Meet Him - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jethalal was about to leave for his shop but he is interrupted with his so-called 'friend' who met him in jail. He suddenly comes to meet Jethalal which scares him and he acts weirdly as Jethalal is alone in the house.

title: Ep. 661 - Daya Is Asked To Give A Testimony - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The police come over to Daya's house. They ask her to give a testimony and appreciate her for her valor and bravery. Jetha refused Daya giving the testimony. What will be the consequences?

title: Ep. 662 - Is Daya In Danger? - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Daya is all set to give her testimony in the court. Jetha is still worried about her safety. Meanwhile, a stranger comes to Jetha's house with some gifts and presents and blackmails them as well.

title: Ep. 663 - A Call From The Underworld - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Daya gets a call, Don Rana, blackmailing her of Jetha's safety. Meanwhile, Jetha gets a call from his shop to come over. Bhide is asked to look after if any strangers enter.

title: Ep. 664 - Jetha's Disguise - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: To escape from any sort of trouble, Jetha disguises himself as an old man. Despite this attempt, he is caught in the act. Meanwhile, Daya is here to rescue him.

title: Ep. 665 - Daya Comes To Rescue - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha is saved when Daya comes over to rescue him. She fights with the gang. The police arrive when the gang escapes. Jetha is furious over the same and they return home.

title: Ep. 666 - Tight Security At Gokuldham - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The police are here at Gokuldham with metal detectors and tight security. Don Rana hasn't given up on his plans and wants to kidnap Daya. Will he be successful?

title: Ep. 667 - Good News For Jetha - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Daya explains the situation she faced with her mother. Meanwhile, Nattu Kaka and Baga come to Jetha's house with the good news of cracking the deal. Don Rana's wife is furious with him and asks him to complete the task.

title: Ep. 668 - Operation 'Kali Billi' - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Rana has asked his men to make sure his brother-in-law returns safely. In the meantime, Jetha asks everybody not to leave their house. But Sodhi takes the children to school.

title: Ep. 669 - The Gang In Gokuldham - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Rana's gang enters Gokuldham society with a smart plan. They watch over Daya and others. Jetha realises there's something fishy and warns the police.

title: Ep. 670 - Sundar Knows The Truth - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: A reportage of the situation in Gokuldham is witnessed by Sundar. Jetha gets a call from Sundar but doesn't want him to know about the situation. Don Rana is in a fix as his wife is still furious with him.

title: Ep. 671 - Jetha's Challenge - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Don Rana calls up Daya. She takes a decision of not giving the testimony which Rana really happy. Jetha, on the other hand challenges Rana.
